  36,68,"Win iwumi Nessi$wzef laĂąmeĂŽ, Neppara yas lxelq amengal. Day ur pxemmimen ara"
  36,69,"Ur as NesseĂȘfev tamedyazt, ur as tlaq. Ayagi, siwa asmekti akked LeqwĂŽan ipbegginen"
  36,70,"Ad inabi win idren, ad iĂ»aĂŽ wawal af ijehliyen"
  36,71,"Day ur walan ara ar Nexleq asen lmal, s ufus nneÂŁ, a ten sĂąun"
  36,72,"Nerra ten d ixdimen nnsen, kra rekben ten, kra teppen ten"
  36,73,"I nitni, segsen, aba$uĂŽ, tissit. Day ur snemmiren ara"
