  36,78,"Ifka yaÂŁ d amedya, ippu lxelq is, inna: \"anwa ara d issidren i$san iu$alen d a$webbaĂŽ"
  36,79,"Ini: \"a ten id Issider Win iten id Ixelqen, abrid amenzu. Neppa IĂ©ĂŽa yal lxelq"
